<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #f4f7f8;
      color: #333;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 850px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 40px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .container:hover {
      background-color: #eaffea; /* light green on hover */
    }

    .page-title {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.8em;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      color: #3498db;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-top: 25px;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    ul li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .bottom-center {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 40px auto;
    }

    .back-btn {
      text-decoration: none;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    .back-btn:hover {
      background-color: #27ae60; /* green on hover */
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .container {
        margin: 20px;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .page-title {
        font-size: 2em;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="page-title">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h1>

    <p>Welcome to the FoodSave FAQ section. Below you'll find answers to the most frequently asked questions about our services.</p>

    <h2>1. What is FoodSave?</h2>
    <p>FoodSave is a platform that helps you save food by connecting consumers with local businesses, restaurants, and grocery stores that have excess food to offer.</p>

    <h2>2. How do I subscribe to FoodSave updates?</h2>
    <p>Simply enter your email address on the homepage or in the newsletter section, and you'll start receiving regular updates.</p>

    <h2>3. How do I unsubscribe from the newsletter?</h2>
    <p>You can unsubscribe at any time by clicking on the unsubscribe link at the bottom of any newsletter email.</p>

    <h2>4. How can I contact FoodSave for support?</h2>
    <p>You can reach out to us via email at <a href="mailto:support@foodsave.org">support@foodsave.org</a> for any support queries.</p>

    <h2>5. Is FoodSave available in all locations?</h2>
    <p>Currently, FoodSave is available in select regions. Please check our website for the most up-to-date availability information.</p>

    <h2>6. How do I report an issue or problem with the platform?</h2>
    <p>If you're experiencing any issues, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@foodsave.org">support@foodsave.org</a> and we'll be happy to assist you.</p>

    <h2>7. Can I suggest new features for the platform?</h2>
    <p>Yes, we value user feedback! Please send us your suggestions or feature requests via email, and we'll consider them for future updates.</p>

    <p><em>Last Updated: April 20, 2025</em></p>
  </div>

  <div class="bottom-center">
    <a href="/" class="back-btn">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
  </div>

</body>
